(ACCOUNT MANAGEMENT POLICY) Tj
T*
(Last updated: January 2025) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(OVERVIEW) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document covers everything related to your customer account: how to create one,) Tj
T*
(how to manage your personal information, security best practices, what happens if you) Tj
T*
(lose access, and your rights regarding account data and deletion.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. CREATING AN ACCOUNT) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Who Can Create an Account) Tj
T*
(Accounts can be created by individuals aged 18 or older \(or the minimum age of) Tj
T*
(majority in your jurisdiction\). By creating an account, you confirm that you meet the) Tj
T*
(age requirement and agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Registration Options) Tj
T*
(You can create an account by:) Tj
T*
(- Registering directly with an email address and password on our website or app) Tj
T*
(- Signing in with Google \(uses your Google account credentials\)) Tj
T*
(- Signing in with Apple \(uses your Apple ID\)) Tj
T*
(- Signing in with Facebook) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When using a social login, we receive only the basic profile information permitted by) Tj
T*
(that platform \(typically your name and email\). We do not receive your social media) Tj
T*
(password.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Account Verification) Tj
T*
(After registration with email and password, a verification email is sent to the) Tj
T*
(address you provided. You must verify your email before you can place orders. The) Tj
T*
(verification link is valid for 48 hours. If it expires, request a new one from the) Tj
T*
(sign-in page.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.4 One Account Per Person) Tj
T*
(Each person may maintain one active account. Creating multiple accounts to circumvent) Tj
T*
(restrictions \(such as one-time promotions or return policy limits\) is a violation of) Tj
T*
(our Terms of Service and may result in all associated accounts being suspended.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. MANAGING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.1 Name and Contact Information) Tj
T*
(Your name and email address can be updated in Account > Personal Information. Email) Tj
T*
(changes require verification of the new address before taking effect.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
