T*
(2.2 Delivery Addresses) Tj
T*
(You can save up to 10 delivery addresses in your address book. Set a default address) Tj
T*
(that is pre-selected at checkout. Addresses are stored securely and never shared with) Tj
T*
(third parties for marketing purposes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.3 Communication Preferences) Tj
T*
(Manage your email preferences in Account > Notifications. Options include:) Tj
T*
(- Order and shipping notifications \(required, cannot be disabled\)) Tj
T*
(- Promotional emails and sale announcements) Tj
T*
(- Subscription reminders and billing alerts) Tj
T*
(- New product announcements) Tj
T*
(- Community forum digests) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(You can also unsubscribe from marketing emails via the unsubscribe link at the bottom) Tj
T*
(of any marketing email. This does not affect transactional emails \(receipts, shipping) Tj
T*
(updates\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.4 Profile Photo) Tj
T*
(An optional profile photo can be uploaded in Account > Personal Information. Photos) Tj
T*
(must be appropriate for a public-facing platform and not include trademarks or) Tj
T*
(copyrighted material.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. ACCOUNT SECURITY) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 Password Requirements) Tj
T*
(Passwords must be at least 8 characters and include at least one uppercase letter,) Tj
T*
(one lowercase letter, one number, and one special character. We recommend using a) Tj
T*
(unique password not used on other services.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 Changing Your Password) Tj
T*
(Go to Account > Security > Change Password. You must enter your current password to) Tj
T*
(set a new one. If you do not know your current password, use the "Forgot Password") Tj
T*
(flow. After a password change, all active sessions on other devices are logged out.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.3 Two-Factor Authentication \(2FA\)) Tj
T*
(We strongly recommend enabling 2FA in Account > Security > Two-Factor Authentication.) Tj
T*
(Options:) Tj
T*
(- SMS code to your phone number) Tj
T*
(- Authenticator app \(Google Authenticator, Authy, or any TOTP-compatible app\)) Tj
T*
(- Email code as a fallback) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When 2FA is enabled, you will be prompted for a verification code at each login.) Tj
T*
(High-value orders may require 2FA verification regardless of whether it is enabled on) Tj
T*
(your account.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.4 Login Activity) Tj
ET
endstream
