72 720 Td
(Review recent login activity in Account > Security > Login History. Each entry shows) Tj
T*
(the date, time, device type, and approximate location. If you see a login you do not) Tj
T*
(recognize, change your password immediately and contact security@shopexample.com.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.5 Session Management) Tj
T*
(You can view and terminate active sessions on other devices in Account > Security >) Tj
T*
(Active Sessions. This is useful if you left yourself logged in on a shared computer.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.6 Suspicious Activity) Tj
T*
(If you receive an email or message claiming to be from us asking for your password,) Tj
T*
(payment info, or personal data, do not respond. We will never ask for your password.) Tj
T*
(Report phishing attempts to security@shopexample.com.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(4. FORGOT PASSWORD AND ACCOUNT RECOVERY) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.1 Forgot Password Flow) Tj
T*
(On the sign-in page, click "Forgot Password" and enter the email address associated) Tj
T*
(with your account. A password reset link will be sent to that email. The link is) Tj
T*
(valid for 1 hour. If you do not receive the email, check spam and ensure you entered) Tj
T*
(the correct address.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Account Locked) Tj
T*
(After 10 consecutive failed login attempts, your account is temporarily locked for 30) Tj
T*
(minutes as a security measure. After the lockout period, you may try again or use the) Tj
T*
(forgot password flow.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.3 Lost Access to Email) Tj
T*
(If you no longer have access to the email address on your account:) Tj
T*
(1. Contact support@shopexample.com from any email address) Tj
T*
(2. Provide: your account email, a recent order number, and the delivery address used) Tj
T*
(on that order) Tj
T*
(3. We will verify your identity using order history and ask security questions) Tj
T*
(4. Upon successful verification, we can update your email address) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For accounts with 2FA enabled, you will also need to provide a backup code \(generated) Tj
T*
(when 2FA was set up\) if your phone is unavailable.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.4 Social Login Recovery) Tj
T*
(If you signed up with Google or Apple and have lost access to that account, contact) Tj
T*
(the respective provider to recover your social account, then use it to log in. If you) Tj
T*
(are unable to recover the social account, contact our support team for manual) Tj
T*
(identity verification.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(5. ORDER HISTORY AND WISHLIST) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
