(5.1 Order History) Tj
T*
(All orders placed while logged into your account are stored in Order History) Tj
T*
(indefinitely. You can view order details, track shipments, initiate returns, and) Tj
T*
(download receipts. Guest orders are not linked to an account.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.2 Wishlist) Tj
T*
(Save items to your Wishlist for future purchase. Wishlists can be made public) Tj
T*
(\(shareable via link\) or private. Public wishlists display only product names and) Tj
T*
(prices ? never your personal details. You can create up to 5 named wishlists.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.3 Recently Viewed) Tj
T*
(Your recently viewed items are stored in your account to personalize your browsing) Tj
T*
(experience. This data is retained for 90 days. You can clear your browsing history in) Tj
T*
(Account > Privacy > Clear Browsing Data.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(6. LOYALTY AND REWARDS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.1 Points Earning) Tj
T*
(Registered account holders earn 1 loyalty point per $1 spent \(excluding taxes,) Tj
T*
(shipping, and gift card purchases\). Points are credited to your account after the) Tj
T*
(return window for the relevant order closes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.2 Points Redemption) Tj
T*
(Points can be redeemed at checkout \(100 points = $1 in discount\). Minimum redemption:) Tj
T*
(500 points. Points cannot be combined with certain promotional discounts \(check terms) Tj
T*
(at checkout\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.3 Points Expiry) Tj
T*
(Points expire 24 months after they are earned if no purchase activity occurs on the) Tj
T*
(account. Making any purchase resets the expiry clock for all accumulated points.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.4 Tier Status) Tj
T*
(Tiers are determined by total spend in a rolling 12-month period:) Tj
T*
(- Silver: $0 to $499 ? base earning rate) Tj
T*
(- Gold: $500 to $1,499 ? 1.25x earning rate, extended returns) Tj
T*
(- Platinum: $1,500 and above ? 1.5x earning rate, priority support, free expedited) Tj
T*
(shipping) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Tier status is evaluated monthly. Dropping below a tier threshold results in) Tj
T*
(reclassification at the next monthly evaluation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(7. ACCOUNT SUSPENSION AND TERMINATION) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.1 Grounds for Suspension) Tj
T*
(We may suspend or terminate accounts that:) Tj
ET
