(- Violate our Terms of Service or any policy) Tj
T*
(- Are associated with fraudulent activity or chargebacks in bad faith) Tj
T*
(- Are used to create fake reviews or manipulate ratings) Tj
T*
(- Abuse promotions, discounts, or the return policy) Tj
T*
(- Attempt to access restricted areas of our systems) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 Notification) Tj
T*
(We will make reasonable efforts to notify you by email before suspending an account,) Tj
T*
(unless the activity poses an immediate security risk or is clearly fraudulent.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 Appealing a Suspension) Tj
T*
(If you believe your account was suspended in error, email appeals@shopexample.com) Tj
T*
(with your account email and a description of the situation. Appeals are reviewed) Tj
T*
(within 5 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(8. ACCOUNT DELETION AND DATA RIGHTS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.1 How to Delete Your Account) Tj
T*
(To request account deletion, go to Account > Privacy > Delete Account, or email) Tj
T*
(privacy@shopexample.com. Deletion requests are processed within 30 days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.2 What Happens to Your Data) Tj
T*
(Upon deletion:) Tj
T*
(- Personal profile information is removed from our systems) Tj
T*
(- Order history is anonymized but retained for legal and financial record-keeping) Tj
T*
(\(typically 7 years\)) Tj
T*
(- Stored payment methods are immediately removed) Tj
T*
(- Wishlist, loyalty points, and subscription are terminated) Tj
T*
(- Any outstanding refunds owed to you will still be processed) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.3 Data Export) Tj
T*
(Before deleting, you can request a copy of your personal data in Account > Privacy >) Tj
T*
(Download My Data. We will prepare a downloadable file within 14 days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.4 Right to Correction) Tj
T*
(You have the right to correct inaccurate personal information stored on your account) Tj
T*
(at any time through Account > Personal Information, or by contacting) Tj
T*
(privacy@shopexample.com.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(9. BUSINESS ACCOUNTS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Business accounts support multiple users under one company profile. Features include) Tj
T*
(consolidated billing, purchase approval workflows, tax-exempt purchasing, and) Tj
T*
(dedicated account management. To set up a business account, email) Tj
T*
(enterprise@shopexample.com or call 1-800-555-0198 \(Business line\).) Tj
ET
